dct_description_sm: Partial cadastral topographic map of District of Columbia beyond former Washington city limits (Florida Avenue).
Relief shown by contours and hachures.
Oriented with north toward the upper left.
Sheets numbered: Sheet No. 1 ... 4, Sheet No. 6; No. 3061 ... 3064, No. 3066. There is no sheet 5.
dct_publisher_sm: United States Coast and Geodetic Survey
